<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>简单起始页 | LambBox</title>
<!-- Load Tailwind CSS -->
<script src="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<!-- Load Inter Font -->
<link href="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2%3Ffamily%3DInter:wght%40400%3B700%3B800%26display%3Dswap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* 保持深色背景和字体 /
body {
font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
background-color: #0d0d15; / 略带深蓝色的深色背景 /
color: #f3f4f6;
}
/ 基础容器居中 */
.container {
max-width: 1200px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">

<!-- 导航栏 -->
<header class="bg-gray-900/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-wider">
            Simple<span class="text-indigo-400">Page</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="space-x-6">
            <a href="#hero" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-indigo-400 transition duration-200">首页</a>
            <a href="#info" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-indigo-400 transition duration-200">更多信息</a>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- 1. 英雄区域 (Hero Section) -->
<main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center text-center py-20 px-4" id="hero">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- 标题，使用渐变色 -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-300 to-white">
            欢迎来到您的新网站
        </h1>
        <!-- 简洁的副标题 -->
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 mb-10">
            这是一个简洁而现代的起始页面，使用 Tailwind CSS 构建，风格为暗黑系。
        </p>
        <!-- 动作按钮 -->
        <button class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
            开始探索
        </button>
    </div>
</main>

<!-- 2. 信息区域 (Info Section) -->
<section id="info" class="py-16 bg-[#181825]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-10">核心价值</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- 卡片 1 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-indigo-500 transition duration-300">
                <div class="text-3xl text-indigo-400 mb-3">🚀</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">高性能</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">提供闪电般的加载速度和卓越的用户体验。</p>
            </div>
            <!-- 卡片 2 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-indigo-500 transition duration-300">
                <div class="text-3xl text-green-400 mb-3">🛡️</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">高安全</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">内置行业领先的安全措施，保护您的数据。</p>
            </div>
            <!-- 卡片 3 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-2xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-indigo-500 transition duration-300">
                <div class="text-3xl text-yellow-400 mb-3">🛠️</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">易于定制</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">简洁的结构使二次开发和定制变得轻松。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- 底部 -->
<footer class="bg-gray-900 py-6 mt-auto border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            © 2025 SimplePage | 保留所有权利。
        </p>
    </div>
</footer>


</body>
</html>
